# Cloudflare Images delivery base URL, e.g. https://imagedelivery.net/<account_hash>
# Public (client-bundled) because the custom image loader in src/lib/cloudflare-image-loader.ts
# runs in both server and client bundles. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your
# account hash — never commit the real value's account hash if you'd rather keep it private,
# though it is not itself sensitive (it only allows reading images you've made public).
NEXT_PUBLIC_CF_IMAGES_DELIVERY_URL=
